Scourge looked up at AzureBlade.... a blood lust began wailing up in him, he 
felt his missile pods opening slowly, and all four arming.... then he saw 
Maxima... and he became calm once more... He stood up and looked at his 
injuries... He felt his mind pulling three different ways, his love of peace, his thirst 
for war, and the unending rage and madness that was slowly begining to wail 
up in his spark... The spark began again and his body jumped to life. 
"Maxima... Somethings wrong..." His eyes began glowing red and he looked at the two as 
the spark within him began to glow white hot...
